<TITLE> Govt invites public view on draft police law </TITLE>
<TEXT>
 Dhaka, Dec 2 (bdnews24.com)  The draft Police Ordinance 2008 has been posted on the website of the home ministry to invite public opinion on issues related to the proposed new law, says a ministry press release on Tuesday. The draft ordinance can be seen and downloaded from www.mha.gov.bd/pdf/policeord08.pdf . Views on the ordinance may be sent to the deputy secretary of the home ministry's law department through the e-mail address: sujaet@gmail.com bd
